high_descs: Go in front of you, then turn left to face the counter with the bread on it.
Pick up the butter knife on the counter, in front of the park.
Turn to the counter at your right.
Put the butter knife in the glass, on the counter.
Pick up the glass from the counter.
Go to the sink, to your right.
Place the glass in the sink basin.
anns.task_desc: Put a glass with a knife in it in the sink.

high_descs: Walk across the room towards the sink, turn left and stop in front of the loaf of bread on the counter.
Pick up the knife that's in front of the pot.
Turn to the right and step closer to the counter with the kettle on it.
Put the knife in the glass next to the kettle on the counter.
Pick up the glass with the knife in it.
Turn to the right and stop in front of the sink.
Place the glass in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place dirty dishes in the sink.

high_descs: Walk to the shelf just above the loaf of bread on the counter.
Pick up the knife in front of the pot on the shelf.
Turn right and look at the counter with the spatula on it.
Place the knife in the cup behind the spatula.
Pick up the cup from the counter.
Turn right and walk to the sink.
Place the cup in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a glass cup with a knife in it into the sink.
